commit.message:
Fix compilation on macOS

Amends: b12602a4690c22c8110b675f8fe1525fdab25fb5

Fix named pipe listen / open

Only one instance can create socket, other instances can only open it.

This fixes issue on Windows when multiple files are opened at once when
QMPlay2 is closed.

This can also fix possibility to open 2 instances when only one instance
is allowed on Windows.
